---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-500">Last updated: May 2026</p>

      <div class="bg-white border border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">By accessing and using paralives-cheats.com, you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">2. Use of Content</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">All content on this website is provided for informational purposes only. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without our written permission.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">3. User Conduct</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">You agree not to use the website for any unlawful purpose or in any way that could damage, disable, or impair the website.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">Paralives is a trademark of its respective owners. This website is not affiliated with or endorsed by the Paralives development team. All game-related content is the property of their respective owners.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">5. Disclaimer</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">The information on this website is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee the accuracy or completeness of any content.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">We shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of the website.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border border-black rounded-2xl p-6 brutal-shadow">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold mb-3">7. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 font-medium text-lg">We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Your continued use of the website constitutes acceptance of any changes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
